name: GoGi House Nguyễn Văn Linh
address: 09, 9 Nguyễn Văn Linh, Phường, Hải Châu, Đà Nẵng 50000

reviews_list.content: We visited on a super busy day and time. It was right at lunch, and their phones were down. We couldnt make a reservation for 8 people. We got there early, and we were able to snag two tables side by side. We did the buffet without seafood. All the ordering is done on an iPad super easy. There is a list for approved buffet items. Then, anything on the other lists would be an additional fee. The meat quality was very good. They provided free refills of kimchi and sides. Its definitely worth the buffet price. Bathrooms are terrible. Dirty and no toilet paper. Floors are slippery walk carefully. Other than that, the food was excellent. Staff was great and attentive. They changed out the grills frequently.

I love the Gogi house for 18 barbecue and it has a nice selection of meat, side dishes noodles and hotpot. You can choose to order separately. Or you can choose the buffet which they have a digital menu on the. Tablet that you can order

Bad overall experience, everytime you begin to cook the meat on the hotplate the staff will come and replace the hot plate with a cold one and ruin the cooking temp of the meat, they do not show the price on the menu with the vat added.

This was definitely the best Korean BBQ restaurant weve dined at here in Vietnam and we cant wait to come back here Thanh Nguyen was the BEST waiter weve ever had the pleasure of meeting and she was absolutely attentive and kind
One of the best BBQ in town. Gogi serves a wide variety of meat . With a wide variety of prices. This place usually full of people at rush hours.
Nice and pleasant place, everything is done to have a good time... special mention to the waitress THANH NGUYEN for her service and her good humor, continue to make the customers laugh, you are great
Buffet ở Gogi House is da best A lot of Juicy Beef and Pork Belly for Lunch. Highly recommended for lunch cuz its not good if Big amount of Protein for night time We love Gogi House
One of the best BBQ in Da Nang. Will be there again next time
Everything was delicious. We enjoyed it. You cook and eat it yourself. The staff is friendly and very helpful.
Gogi House was a nice setting with good food. What made it really good was the service from Thanh Nguyên She was very helpful and nice.

reviews_list.content: Air conditioner so low , area so hot, food no fresh, not really cheaper price

Even as a foreigner who cant speak Vietnamese, this restaurant offer a sushi conveyer belt style all you can eat mini hotpot, not much interaction is required with the staff, just fill your stomach and pay the bill, the place is very clean.

Highly recommend this restaurant The hotpots, particularly the Tomyum hotspot were superb and delicious and the seafood was super fresh. The staff was very cute and enthusiastic, service was speedy. Also, the price is very reasonable for everyone.
